description: Regenerates the primary or secondary connection strings for the specified Namespace.

resource_group_name.description: Name of the resource group within the azure subscription.

parameters.description: Parameters required to regenerate the connection string.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials that uniquely identify a Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

key.description: Optional, if the key value provided, is set for KeyType or autogenerated Key value set for keyType
